#: src-en/data/events_special_boons.xml.append:2
msgid ""
"data/events_special_boons.xml.append$//event[@name=\"BOON_SELECT_DEEPONE\"]/text"
msgstr ""
"不知从哪里，你听到一个声音在对你说话。“恩...深渊。你的敌人...开启时移动速度会"
"减慢10%...你的船。你可以...感谢之前的挑战者。或者是你...不要吗？谁能说……”"

#: src-en/data/events_special_boons.xml.append:5
msgid ""
"data/events_special_boons.xml.append$//event[@name=\"BOON_SELECT_DEEPONE\"]/choice/text"
msgstr "继续。"

#: src-en/data/events_special_boons.xml.append:13
msgid ""
"data/events_special_boons.xml.append$//event[@name=\"BOON_SELECT_DDSOULPLAGUE_CREW\"]/text"
msgstr ""
"不知从何处，你听见一个声音对你说道：“吞噬者恩惠……与灵魂瘟疫结盟的船员……在你的"
"船上移动速度将提升30%。你可以……感谢上一位挑战者。或许你……并不想感谢？谁又知道"
"呢……”"

#: src-en/data/events_special_boons.xml.append:16
msgid ""
"data/events_special_boons.xml.append$//event[@name=\"BOON_SELECT_DDSOULPLAGUE_CREW\"]/choice/text"
msgstr "继续。"

#: src-en/data/events_special_boons.xml.append:24
msgid ""
"data/events_special_boons.xml.append$//event[@name=\"BOON_SELECT_DDDEEPONE_ELITE\"]/text"
msgstr ""
"不知从何处传来一个声音，对你说道：“深渊之赐……深渊潜者们……会使附近敌人的技能充"
"能速率……每个降低50%。你可以……感谢上一位挑战者。或许你……并不想感谢？谁又知道呢"
"……”"

#: src-en/data/events_special_boons.xml.append:27
msgid ""
"data/events_special_boons.xml.append$//event[@name=\"BOON_SELECT_DDDEEPONE_ELITE\"]/choice/text"
msgstr "继续。"

#: src-en/data/events_special_boons.xml.append:35
msgid ""
"data/events_special_boons.xml.append$//event[@name=\"BOON_SELECT_DDSERAPHIM_CREW\"]/text"
msgstr ""
"不知从何处传来一个声音，对你说道：“天穹之赐……你的船员……会使附近敌人所受的火焰"
"伤害……每个提升20%。你可以……感谢上一位挑战者。或许你……并不想感谢？谁又知道呢……"
"”"

#: src-en/data/events_special_boons.xml.append:38
msgid ""
"data/events_special_boons.xml.append$//event[@name=\"BOON_SELECT_DDSERAPHIM_CREW\"]/choice/text"
msgstr "继续。"

#: src-en/data/events_special_boons.xml.append:46
msgid ""
"data/events_special_boons.xml.append$//event[@name=\"BOON_SELECT_DDCORRUPTOR\"]/text"
msgstr ""
"不知从何处传来一个声音，对你说道：“腐化赐福……正——正在安装。安装完成！赐福效果"
"：灵魂瘟疫潮生命值+5。若——你——曾见过上一位挑战者；请致以谢意。我建议你——也来—"
"—见见我。”"

#: src-en/data/events_special_boons.xml.append:49
msgid ""
"data/events_special_boons.xml.append$//event[@name=\"BOON_SELECT_DDCORRUPTOR\"]/choice/text"
msgstr "继续。"

#: src-en/data/events_special_boons.xml.append:57
msgid ""
"data/events_special_boons.xml.append$//event[@name=\"BOON_SELECT_DEEPONE_EQUIPMENT\"]/text"
msgstr ""
"不知从何处传来一个声音，对你说道：“挑战者！我赐予你恐惧之祝福！你将有20%的概"
"率抵抗离子伤害，愿你的旅途蒙受祝福！你该感谢谁？当然是上一位挑战者！哈哈哈！”"

#: src-en/data/events_special_boons.xml.append:60
msgid ""
"data/events_special_boons.xml.append$//event[@name=\"BOON_SELECT_DEEPONE_EQUIPMENT\"]/choice/text"
msgstr "继续。"

#: src-en/data/events_special_boons.xml.append:68
msgid ""
"data/events_special_boons.xml.append$//event[@name=\"BOON_SELECT_DISPARITY_EQUIPMENT\"]/text"
msgstr ""
"不知从何处传来一个声音，对你说道：“挑战者！我赐予你贪婪黑暗之祝福！你的饥饿暗"
"影生命值增加10点，愿你的旅途蒙受祝福！你该感谢谁？当然是上一位挑战者！哈哈哈"
"！”"

#: src-en/data/events_special_boons.xml.append:71
msgid ""
"data/events_special_boons.xml.append$//event[@name=\"BOON_SELECT_DISPARITY_EQUIPMENT\"]/choice/text"
msgstr "继续。"

#: src-en/data/events_special_boons.xml.append:79
msgid ""
"data/events_special_boons.xml.append$//event[@name=\"BOON_SELECT_DDSOULPLAGUE_EQUIPMENT\"]/text"
msgstr ""
"不知从何处传来一个声音，对你说道：“挑战者！我赐予你幻彩腐化之祝福！你的灵魂瘟"
"疫躯壳受到的火焰伤害将降低为0.25倍，愿你的旅途蒙受祝福！你该感谢谁？当然是上"
"一位挑战者！哈哈哈！”"

#: src-en/data/events_special_boons.xml.append:82
msgid ""
"data/events_special_boons.xml.append$//event[@name=\"BOON_SELECT_DDSOULPLAGUE_EQUIPMENT\"]/choice/text"
msgstr "继续。"

#: src-en/data/events_special_boons.xml.append:90
msgid ""
"data/events_special_boons.xml.append$//event[@name=\"BOON_SELECT_DDFALSERADIANCE_EQUIPMENT\"]/text"
msgstr ""
"不知从何处传来一个声音，对你说道：“挑战者！我赐予你陨落恩典之祝福！你的光裔族"
"破门速度提升一倍，愿你的旅途蒙受祝福！你该感谢谁？当然是上一位挑战者！哈哈哈"
"！”"

#: src-en/data/events_special_boons.xml.append:93
msgid ""
"data/events_special_boons.xml.append$//event[@name=\"BOON_SELECT_DDFALSERADIANCE_EQUIPMENT\"]/choice/text"
msgstr "继续。"
